that's really appreciated.

5
00:00:15,867 --> 00:00:17,907
I'm gonna be talking at length about how to make

6
00:00:18,347 --> 00:00:21,408
bored millennials play your text games

7
00:00:21,448 --> 00:00:23,689
instead of shooting aliens in the head.

8
