13
00:00:39,679 --> 00:00:42,743
So, text in video games. It all sounds a little bit 1977, doesn't it?

14
00:00:44,915 --> 00:00:48,177
But as we know, text games have been making something of a comeback,

15
00:00:48,697 --> 00:00:54,000
in no small part because of the rise of mobiles and tablets,

16
00:00:54,201 --> 00:00:56,022
a great form factor for reading.

17
00:00:56,042 --> 00:00:59,384
We're seeing text games everywhere, on PC,

18
00:01:00,084 --> 00:01:03,526
and we, as a company, are even making, at Inkle,

19
